I'll jump right off this roof.


759
0:55:5,362 --> 0:55:30,524
Oh, Tony!
Yes!


760
0:55:30,524 --> 0:55:32,251
Aw, gee, I'm happy.


761
0:55:32,251 --> 0:55:39,95
Aren't you?
Yes.


762
