0:55:47,78 --> 0:55:50,523
I think you're on the level.
You bet I'm on the level, Miss Darling.


765
0:55:50,523 --> 0:55:52,617
You gotta be good to my little girl.


766
0:55:52,617 --> 0:55:55,752
She's just a baby.
Don't worry about that.


767
0:55:55,752 --> 0:55:57,506
She'll love it out in the country.


768
0:55:57,506 --> 0:55:59,671
