771
0:56:6,95 --> 0:56:8,57
My baby angel.


772
0:56:8,57 --> 0:56:10,953
What's the next thing on the program?


773
0:56:10,953 --> 0:56:14,206
Why, I thought we all might all have dinner
some place to celebrate.


774
0:56:14,206 --> 0:56:16,704
Where? You gotta make it early.
I have a show.


775
0:56:16,704 --> 0:56:19,134
How about that chop suey place
we was at the other night?


776
0:56:19,134 --> 0:56:20,798
That's fine.
Okay, about six?


777
0:56:20,798 --> 0:56:23,487
Great. Well, I'll be running along.


778
0:56:23,487 --> 0:56:31,151
Goodbye for a little while, sweetheart.


779
0:56:31,151 --> 0:56:36,883
Oh, excuse me.


780
0:56:36,883 --> 0:56:48,271
You're all right, son.


781
0:56:48,271 --> 0:56:52,3
Was that the boyfreind we've been hearing so much about
