and Gus is all set to can ya.


820
0:58:17,638 --> 0:58:18,778
You're a dirty liar.


821
0:58:18,778 --> 0:58:21,675
All right. Phone Gus
and find out for yourself.


822
0:58:21,675 --> 0:58:23,528
Well, I'm certainly going to call you
on that one.


823
0:58:23,528 --> 0:58:26,433
Bryant 9483.


824
0:58:26,433 --> 0:58:28,888
We'll just have a little showdown around here.


825
0:58:28,888 --> 0:58:30,78
It will suit me fine.


826
0:58:30,78 --> 0:58:32,959
Hello, I want to speak to Gus Weinbaum.
This is Miss Darling.


827
0:58:32,959 --> 0:58:34,664
Hello, Kitty?


828
0:58:34,664 --> 0:58:36,38
What's on your mind?


829
0:58:36,38 --> 0:58:39,69
What's this I hear about you not renewing my contract
after the show tonight?


830
0:58:39,69 --> 0:58:42,62
Well, you haven't got that quite right, Kitty.


831
0:58:42,62 --> 0:58:45,85
The fact is I got Lou working on a book now...


832
0:58:45,85 --> 0:58:46,941
called "The Boarding School Girls".


833
0:58:46,941 --> 0:58:49,858
And it's gotta have somebody in it that's young.


834
0:58:49,858 --> 0:58:51,957
An ingenue lead, see?


835
0:58:51,957 --> 0:58:55,295
Ingenue lead? I know the stuff the boys
there out front want...


836
0:58:55,295 --> 0:58:57,295
I don't know why you shouldn't write
that book around me.


837
0:58:57,295 --> 0:58:59,327
You're not gonna be left out.


838
0:58:59,327 --> 0:59:3,295
I got you down for a specialty number
and a runway number...


839
0:59:3,295 --> 0:59:5,14
so where do you get in to squawk?


840
0:59:5,14 --> 0:59:7,259
I'm a liar, eh?


841
0:59:7,259 --> 0:59:8,795
I'll show Gus where he gets off.


842
0:59:8,795 --> 0:59:11,148
I'll have a contract in my own terms
in ten minutes.


843
0:59:11,148 --> 0:59:13,836
Hello, girlie, get me Bryant 9400.


844
0:59:13,836 --> 0:59:16,68
Hello, I wanna speak to Dave Holtz.


845
0:59:16,68 --> 0:59:18,544
I'll show the dirty little...
Hello, Dave.


846
0:59:18,544 --> 0:59:19,976
This is Kitty Darling.


847
0:59:19,976 --> 0:59:23,55
Say, Dave, I'm closing
with Parisian Flirts tonight.


848
0:59:23,55 --> 0:59:26,283
How about grabbing yourself a real bet
for your Summer Widows?


849
0:59:26,283 --> 0:59:30,2
Thought I'd give you first crack
instead of fooling around with other stuff.


850
0:59:30,2 --> 0:59:32,988
Well, you better take him.


851
0:59:32,988 --> 0:59:45,29
